# DockAccessory.TrackingState

**Structure**

A representation of the active tracking session state.

## Declaration

```swift
struct TrackingState
```

## Overview

The active tracking session emits this state 10 times per second.

## Instance Properties

- **description**
- **time**: The timestamp indicating when the dock captured the tracking state.
- **trackedSubjects**: A collection of actively tracked subjects.

## Conforms To

- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
